Multiobjective Module 
=====================
`SAES` now has the capability to generate the pareto front for multiobjective optimization problems. The pareto front is generated for a specific metric and instance in 2D, 3D, or higher dimensions. 
Here are some code examples showcasing the use of the multiobjective module.
